  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/UIKit\/UIFontDescriptor\/AttributeName\/fixedAdvance\ncrawled: 2025-12-05T04:00:29Z\n---\n\n# fixedAdvance\n\n**Type Property**\n\nThe glyph advancement attribute.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstatic let fixedAdvance: UIFontDescriptor.AttributeName\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nThe value is an [doc:\/\/com.apple.documentation\/documentation\/Foundation\/NSNumber] instance that contains a float value. This float value overrides the glyph advancement that the font specifies. The default value is `0.0`.\n\n## Constants\n\n- **cascadeList**: The cascading list attribute.\n- **characterSet**: The character set attribute.\n- **face**: The font face attribute.\n- **family**: The font family attribute.\n- **featureSettings**: The font feature settings attribute.\n- **matrix**: The font’s transformation matrix attribute.\n- **name**: The font name attribute.\n- **size**: The font size attribute.\n- **textStyle**: The text style attribute.\n- **traits**: The font traits dictionary attribute.\n- **visibleName**: The font’s visible name attribute.\n\n",
